data.description: Charming gem nestled in a tranquil and desirable neighborhood. Moments away from city conveniences to your local grocery, resturants and medical care. Hwy 1604 and 410 near by. This meticulously maintained 1982-built home boasts a spacious 1,413 sq ft new flooring throughout the house, featuring granite counter tops and new island in kitchen with natural light  with bay windows ,delightful fireplace for any ambiance and mature trees providing natural shade and creating a serene atmosphere for any landscaping. Rooms are spacious for any of your dream use. Welcome home to a timeless retreat that combines modern amenities with lots of charm to make your masterpiece.
